data.description: CORNER LOT!!! Located just minutes from Bay Front Restaurants, Pensacola's Bay Center, the Saenger Theater, Blue Wahoos Stadium & NAS.  This home offers everything you desire. The "Elston" is the perfect Two-Story, 4 BDR Floor plan with a roomy Bonus Loft! Kitchen is a Gourmet's Delight with Birch Cabinets, an over-sized Island within the Breakfast Bar, drop-in Stainless Steel Sink, full console dishwasher, powerful garbage disposal, free-standing coil-top range, vented hood & nice size pantry.  Kitchen is open to great room which makes this home excellent for entertaining. Half-Bath Powder room on the first level is perfect for when you have guests.  Master suite features Shower, a huge Walk-in Closet,  Double Vanities, and a  Separate Water Closet. Outside features a 2-Car Double Garage, low maintenance vinyl siding , designer landscaping, and Hurricane Fabric Shield Protection .
data.whatILove: Granite counter tops in kitchen, recessed lighting and decorator lights over huge kitchen island. Walk in pantry. Wood look designer tile throughout the ground floor. New carpet on second floor. Cozy conversation nook on second floor. Mammoth walk-closet and shower with seat.
